Bernard H. TABOR, Appellant, v. William H. HARDWICK, Warden, U. S. Penitentiary, Atlanta, Georgia, Appellee. No. 15477. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. May 20, 1955. Rehearing Denied July 22, 1955. See 224 F.2d 526. No appearance for appellant. James W. Dorsey, U. S. Atty., Harvey H. Tisinger, Asst. U. S. Atty., Atlanta, Ga., for appellee.

Before RIVES and CAMERON, Circuit Judges, and DAWKINS, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment appealed from is Affirmed.
